x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">To that end, ARTDAI=
 was able to chart the average price of auction lots compared with total au=
ction volume. For the most part, average prices rise and fall <i>with </i>s=
ales volume, but that=E2=80=99s often because there are more high-value wor=
ks being sold when dollar volume rises. Again, this all gets back to sentim=
ent: More sellers will test the market when the market, in their eyes, seem=
s worth testing.</td>
